@startuml
!include ../../_common/style.puml

title Future Provider 扩展组件关系图

left to right direction

package "Provider SPI" as spi {
  interface LockProvider
}

package "Phase 2 - Fencing Token" as phase2 {
  interface FencingTokenProvider <<phase2>>
  class RedisIncrFencingTokenProvider <<phase2>>
  class DbSequenceFencingTokenProvider <<phase2>>
}

package "Phase 3 - Strong Coordination Provider" as phase3 {
  class ZkLockProvider <<phase3>>
  class EtcdLockProvider <<phase3>>
}

LockProvider <|.. ZkLockProvider
LockProvider <|.. EtcdLockProvider

FencingTokenProvider <|.. RedisIncrFencingTokenProvider
FencingTokenProvider <|.. DbSequenceFencingTokenProvider

note right of FencingTokenProvider
  二期能力：
  为成功加锁生成单调递增 fencing token。

  可选实现：
  - Redis INCR
  - DB sequence
  - 独立 token table
end note

note right of ZkLockProvider
  三期能力：
  - 临时节点
  - 顺序节点
  - 公平锁
  - 强协调
end note

note right of EtcdLockProvider
  三期能力：
  - lease
  - revision
  - watch
  - 选主 / 控制面协调
end note

@enduml
